    index = sequence.index('0')
    return sequence[:index] + '0' + sequence[index:-1]

def transform(sequence):
    first_digit = sequence[0]
    last_digit = sequence[-1]
    middle_digits = sequence[1:-1]
    
    return first_digit + middle_digits.replace('0', '') + last_digit + '0'*(len(sequence)-len(first_digit)-len(middle_digits)-len(last_digit))
